The package ncurses is compatible with built-in CMake variables:

    set(CURSES_NEED_NCURSES TRUE)
    find_package(Curses REQUIRED)
    target_include_directories(main PRIVATE ${CURSES_INCLUDE_DIRS})
    target_compile_options(main PRIVATE ${CURSES_CFLAGS})
    target_link_libraries(main PRIVATE ${CURSES_LIBRARIES})

On macOS in this overlay:

    - System ncurses staging is used for static linkage.
    - Dynamic linkage skips system staging and uses the source-build path.
    - You may override ncurses discovery with VCPKG_NCURSES_SYSTEM_PREFIX.
    - If VCPKG_NCURSES_SYSTEM_PREFIX is set, it must contain a usable ncurses installation.
